name: rikoprayitno & rionovtriansyah - Blast Off!!
description:
In search of balance in life, I decided to wander. Looking for another possibility to another dimension. I believe there are many souls out there who are synergizing with my good cause.
in each adventure later I will send a postcard sent to my home address. When I return home, everything will be recorded in one journal.
On this day me, iki, and rio will start this journey. Maybe at some crossroads, we will meet.
cheers
